Ingredients
1 (5lb) duck 
A few stalks of fresh herbs. 
5 cloves garlic 
Green onion
Plenty of salt
Some honey for basting

1-2 tablespoons olive oil
1 cup minced green onion
1 1/2 cups (350ml) red wine
2 tablespoons red wine vinegar
15 figs preserved in honey
15 dates 
Salt
